<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>qd bdạ ạ̉mr ʿjyb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- qad̊ badā ạảm̊ruⁿ ʿajībuⁿ
 bitajasũdi ạlại̹lah̊
 yā laniʿ̊maẗiⁿ tajalãt̊
 biạlṣãlībi lil̊kẖuṭāh̊

[V2]
 2- kāna ʿad̊lạaⁿ ạản̊ tadīna
 ạl̊kulã ại̹dẖ̊ zugẖ̊nā maʿā
 lakini ạl̊ḥuk̊ma qabil̊ta
 ạản̊ta ʿanãạ ạảj̊maʿā

[V3]
 3- maʿ̊ka biạlrũwḥi juʿil̊nā
 wāḥidaⁿạ mil̊yaⁿ̉ạ laka
 yā lahu siraⁿ̃ạ ʿaẓīmaⁿạ
 nuṣ̊biḥu jasadaka

[V4]
 4- ḥas̊ba qaṣ̊diⁿ fī ạldũhūri
 ḥik̊maẗuⁿ tanawãʿat̊
 yā laniʿ̊maẗiⁿ tajalãt̊
 yā laḥik̊maẗiⁿ samat̊

[V5]
 5- fayuʿarãfu ạlsãlạṭīnu
 binā wālrũwảsā
 ḥik̊maẗa ạllhi ạlãtī qad̊
 ạủʿ̊linat̊ mina ạlsãmā

[V6]
 6- mus̊taḥiquⁿ kulã sẖuk̊riⁿ
 wasujūdiⁿ watẖanā
 waʿibādaẗiⁿ waḥam̊diⁿ
 lildũhūri rabãnā</lyrics>
</song>